text: František Wirth (7 March 1915 - 1 June 2003) was a Czech gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:2003 deaths Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Prague
